里，闭上眼也能听到呓语，于是不敢自己独自居住，跑到闺蜜家求助。 到达后她已经语无伦次，任凭闺蜜如何问询，都无法说明原因，就这样熬过了两天后，闺蜜实在受不了带着她前往医院，经过医生检查，确认其为神经精神型野生菌中毒。 医生介绍称，见手青中毒的患者可表现为幻觉，甚至被害妄想，对于这类患者，没有特效药，主要是对症治疗，安抚镇静后予以催吐、洗胃。 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-edf77f54afc758652819f1bba73136c3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "22 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660647354"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8r6HpMXloqo7EAMaCTEwOTA4ODE1MyDo4pS0BjAAOF5AGHIJNjYwNjQ3MzU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1720140973.63170", "card_id": "Q_25066063", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 60}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些奇特口味的冰激凌？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "看到大家都在爆奇特口味的月饼，忽然想到我吃过的榴莲香菜冰激凌，这酸爽… 大家吃过什么奇特口味的冰激凌？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-eacc2e0eb82ed51580585d528cba786d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "22 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/25066063"}}, "attached_info": "CjwI8r6HpMXloqo7EAMaBzIyMDg0NjQghdGPoAUwADhvQBlyCDI1MDY2MDYzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1720140973.65569", "card_id": "Q_630382600", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么《英雄联盟》里没有 AD 帽子？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "为什么在《英雄联盟》这款游戏里 AP 装备拥有帽子这种纯粹加法强的装备 而 AD 装备却没有呢"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-37534aa7ff094e9fb4758f7307385bf9_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "22 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/630382600"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8r6H